content:
Enhance your Mobile Publisher app with new security features, such as user opt-in biometric login (beta) and custom mobile security policies. To meet Google’s requirements for push notifications on Android, submit your app’s Firebase information.

Mobile Publisher retired Android app distribution through the Managed Public option in Winter ’23. Existing Mobile Publisher Android apps distributed with this option continue to work but no longer receive updates.

Experience Cloud Apps Now Require Android 8 or iOS 16 and Later

Set Up Opt-In Biometric Login for Fast and Secure Experience Cloud App Logins (Beta)

Configure How Your Experience Cloud App Responds to Security Threats

Binary Upload Is the Default Distribution Method for New Mobile Publisher Apps

Add Links to an Experience Cloud iOS App’s Login Page

Set the Default Method for How Your Experience Cloud App Opens External URLs

Simplify Site Navigation on Mobile Publisher for LWR Sites (Beta)

Privacy Manifests Are Now Generated for Experience Cloud iOS Apps
title: Enhance Mobile Publisher Security Features
